 The Voidz 分享新专辑《Like All Before You》的更多细节，并发布大气开场曲《Overture》 https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-voidz-share-more-details-on-new-album-like-all-before-you-release-atmospheric-opener-overture-3772961?utm_source= rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=the-voidz-share-more-details-on-new-album-like-all-before-release-atmospheric-opener-overtureAnagricel Duran Mon, 08 Jul 2024 16:08:08 +0000 Music NewsNewsIndieLive Music NewsRock https://www.nme.com/?p=3772961 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/The-Voidz.-Credit_-Cheryl-Georgette.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="虚空。图片来源：谢丽尔·乔吉特" decoding="async" fetchpriority="high" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/The-Voidz.-Credit_-Cheryl-Georgette.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/The-Voidz.-Credit_-Cheryl-Georgette-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/The-Voidz.-Credit_-Cheryl-Georgette-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/The-Voidz.-Credit_-Cheryl-Georgette-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/The-Voidz.-Credit_-Cheryl-Georgette-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/The-Voidz.-Credit_-Cheryl-Georgette-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>乐队还透露了在纽约和洛杉矶的一系列现场演出</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-voidz-share-more-details-on-new-album-like-all-before-you-release-atmospheric-opener-overture-3772961">The Voidz 的帖子分享了有关新专辑《Like All Before You》的更多细节，发布大气开场曲《Overture》</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/The-Voidz.-Credit_-Cheryl-Georgette.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="虚空。图片来源：谢丽尔·乔吉特" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/The-Voidz.-Credit_-Cheryl-Georgette.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/The-Voidz.-Credit_-Cheryl-Georgette-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/The-Voidz.-Credit_-Cheryl-Georgette-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/The-Voidz.-Credit_-Cheryl-Georgette-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/The-Voidz.-Credit_-Cheryl-Georgette-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/The-Voidz.-Credit_-Cheryl-Georgette-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="/artists/The-Voidz">The Voidz</a>宣布推出他们的第三张专辑《Like All Before You》，并分享了该唱片的开场曲《Overture》。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/blogs/nme-blogs/10-best-side-projects-indie-gorillaz-voidz-last-shadow-puppets-2622373">从《猩猩》到《最后的皮影》：独立游戏中 10 个最佳副业项目</a></strong></li></ul><p>本周早些时候，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/julian-casablancas">朱利安·卡萨布兰卡斯</a>和他的同事。分享了专辑的神秘预告视频，乐队透露了唱片的发行日期，并由充满喜怒无常的合成器的器乐“序曲”配乐，这是专辑的开场曲。</p><p>现在，乐队宣布他们的第三张专辑《Like All Before You》将于 9 月 20 日以数字方式发行，并将于 10 月 18 日开始在 Vinyl 上发售（<a href="https://onerpm.link/likeallbeforeyou" target="_blank" rel="noopener">您可以在此处预先保存</a>）。 《Like All Before You》是在乐队位于加利福尼亚州威尼斯的家庭工作室以及洛杉矶著名的 Vox 工作室创作的。</p><p>这张唱片中，乐队与制作人 Ivan Wayman（ <a href="/artists/Beyonce">Beyoncé</a> 、 <a href="/artists/Miley-Cyrus">Miley Cyrus</a> 、 <a href="/artists/The-War-on-Drugs">The War on Drugs</a> ）、Justin Raisen（ <a href="/artists/Yeah-Yeah-yeahs">Yeah Yeah Yeahs</a> 、 <a href="/artists/Kim-Gordon">Kim Gordon</a> 、 <a href="/artists/Yves-Tumor">Yves Tumor</a> ）和 SAD PONY（ <a href="/artists/Lil-Yachty">Lil Yachty</a> 、 <a href="/artists/Drake">Drake</a> ）合作制作了多首歌曲。 </p><p><iframe title="The Voidz - 序曲（官方音频）" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/GnfmyiUY6YE?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><figure id="attachment_3772979" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3772979" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3772979" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/The-Voidz-Like-All-Before-You-album-artwork.-Credit-PRES.jpg" alt="Voidz 《Like All Before You》专辑封面。图片来源：新闻界" width="2000" height="1988" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/The-Voidz-Like-All-Before-You-album-artwork.-Credit-PRES.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/The-Voidz-Like-All-Before-You-album-artwork.-Credit-PRES-150x150.jpg 150w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/The-Voidz-Like-All-Before-You-album-artwork.-Credit-PRES-400x398.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/The-Voidz-Like-All-Before-You-album-artwork.-Credit-PRES-800x795.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/The-Voidz-Like-All-Before-You-album-artwork.-Credit-PRES-696x692.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/The-Voidz-Like-All-Before-You-album-artwork.-Credit-PRES-1392x1384.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/The-Voidz-Like-All-Before-You-album-artwork.-Credit-PRES-1068x1062.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3772979" class="wp-caption-text"> Voidz 《Like All Before You》专辑封面。图片来源：新闻界</figcaption></figure><h3><strong>《喜欢你之前的一切》曲目列表：</strong></h3><p> <strong>1.《序曲》</strong><br /> <strong>2.“方波”</strong><br /> <strong>3.《龙的预言》</strong><br /> <strong>4.《七匹马》</strong><br /> <strong>5.“光谱分析”</strong><br /> <strong>6.“屈魔师”</strong><br /> <strong>7.“坚持——1C2S”</strong><br /> <strong>8.“都一样”</strong><br /> <strong>9.“这些混蛋的时代什么时候结束”</strong><br /> <strong>10.《走开（尾声）》</strong></p><p>乐队在万圣节前夕推出的《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/listen-to-the-voidz-spooky-new-single-flexorcist-3524121">Flexorcist</a> 》和金属流行音乐《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/listen-to-the-voidz-metallic-pop-track-prophecy-of-the-dragon-3448647">Prophecy of the Dragon</a> 》（乐队去年 10 月将这两首歌曲合并成 14 分钟的音乐录影带）都将出现在 LP 中。</p><p>在其他地方，卡萨布兰卡斯和合作者还宣布在纽约和洛杉矶举行两场演出，以庆祝《Like All Before You》的发行。他们将于 10 月 16 日接管洛杉矶的欧菲姆剧院，并于 10 月 18 日接管纽约哈莱姆区的阿波罗剧院。门票预售将于当地时间 7 月 11 日星期四上午 10 点进行。一般门票销售将于 7 月 12 日星期五上午 10 点开始。 <a href="https://ticketmaster.evyy.net/c/2862475/264167/4272?sharedid=NME&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ticketmaster.com%2Fthe-voidz-tickets%2Fartist%2F2046291" target="_blank" rel="noopener">请访问此处购买门票</a>。</p><h3> <strong>The Voidz 2024 年美国直播日期为：</strong></h3><p><strong>十月</strong><br /><strong>16 - 洛杉矶，奥珀汉姆剧院</strong><br /><strong>18 – 纽约，阿波罗剧院</strong></p><p>Voidz 的最新作品是 2018 年的《Virtue》，紧接着他们 2014 年的首张作品《Tyranny》。在<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/the-voidz-virtue-review-2273640">四星评价</a>中， <em>《NME</em> 》的 Rhian Daly 称这张唱片是“有趣、不寻常且发人深省”的作品，但并没有“失去其古怪的发明家风格”，“其中出现了一些流行音乐的时刻”。突破界限的。”</p><p>与此同时，卡萨布兰卡斯作为<a href="/artists/The-Strokes">The Strokes</a>的一部分继续保持活跃。去年，乐队在伦敦与 Angel Olsen、Yeah Yeah Yeahs、The Walkmen、Girl in Red 和 The Strokes 等乐队一起演出<a href="https://www.nme.com/festivals/all-points-east">All Point East</a> 。在三月份支持芝加哥国会候选人基娜·柯林斯 (Kina Collins) 的一场演出中， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-the-strokes-dust-off-live-rarities-at-kina-collins-benefit-gig-in-chicago-3599528">The Strokes 重演了几首现场罕见曲目</a>，其中包括《Room on Fire》剪辑版《You Talk Way Too Much》。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-voidz-share-more-details-on-new-album-like-all-before-you-release-atmospheric-opener-overture-3772961">The Voidz 的帖子分享了有关新专辑《Like All Before You》的更多细节，发行大气的开场曲《Overture》</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
观看 Garbage 和 Peaches 在柏林表演“Push It”和“Fuck The Pain Away”混搭https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-garbage-and-peaches-perform-push-it-and-fuck-the-pain-away-3772980?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=watch-garbage-和桃子执行推它和他妈的痛苦Liberty DunworthMon, 08 Jul 2024 16:08:07 +0000 Music NewsNewsAlternativeRock https://www.nme.com/?p=3772980 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Garbage-Peaches@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="Peaches 和 Garbage 乐队的雪莉·曼森 (Shirley Manson) 将于 2024 年演出。" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Garbage-Peaches@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Garbage-Peaches@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Garbage-Peaches@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Garbage-Peaches@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Garbage-Peaches@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Garbage-Peaches@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “她是一个按照自己的方式做所有事情并撕毁了她之前的所有废话规则的人”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-garbage-and-peaches-perform-push-it-and-fuck-the-pain-away-3772980">Watch Garbage 和 Peaches 在柏林表演“Push It”和“Fuck The Pain Away”混搭后，</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Garbage-Peaches@2000x1270.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="Peaches 和 Garbage 乐队的雪莉·曼森 (Shirley Manson) 将于 2024 年演出。" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Garbage-Peaches@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Garbage-Peaches@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Garbage-Peaches@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Garbage-Peaches@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Garbage-Peaches@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Garbage-Peaches@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/garbage">Garbage</a>与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/peaches">Peaches</a>联手，在最近的一场现场表演中带来了《Push It》和《Fuck The Pain Away》的爆炸性混搭。查看下面的合作片段。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/garbages-shirley-manson-interview-bleed-like-me-dave-grohl-new-album-industry-3614427">Garbage 的雪莉·曼森 (Shirley Manson)：“我们正在失去来自工人阶级出身和敢于冒险的乐队”</a></strong></li></ul><p>这一时刻发生在上周（7 月 4 日）Garbage 登上德国舞台，并在柏林音乐厅上演了一场盛大的头条秀。</p><p>在演出的最后，他们演唱了《Only Happy When It Rains》、《#1 Crush》和《I Think I&#39;m Paranoid》等热门歌曲，主唱<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/shirley-manson">雪莉·曼森 (Shirley Manson)</a>戏弄观众说，“非常特别”嘉宾将加入乐队，在安可前演唱最后一首歌曲。</p><p> “我们要再给你播放一首歌曲，我只是想让你知道，你将面对摇滚乐皇室成员，”她开始面对音乐界女性所面临的挣扎当她开始她的职业生涯时所面临的。</p><p> “这位女王会在某个适合她的时候摇摆不定，但我只想说这一点，因为我不能让今晚不提这一点就过去。当你是一个 90 年代出现的乐队中的女性时，你并没有得到很多人的支持。</p><p> “当时有很多厌恶女性的媒体，非常重男轻女，为音乐杂志撰稿的女性并不多。主要是男性。我对此不太满意，”曼森解释道。</p><p> “这个人是一个伟大的人——不仅是一个支持者，而且是一个安慰者、一个女巫同伴、一个生活和音乐的热爱者。她充满热情，相信一切美好和伟大的事情。今晚她能来加入我们，我感到非常荣幸。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Garbage x Peaches - Push It / Fuck The Pain Away（柏林音乐厅，2024 年 7 月 4 日）现场/高清" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/Cu7HwHIbIN4?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> “她是一个非常非常特别的人。一切都按照她自己的方式去做，并打破了她出现在音乐舞台之前的所有废话规则。”</p><p>从那时起，Garbage 开始表演“Push It”——这是他们 1998 年第二张专辑“Version 2.0”中的一首歌曲。曼森还将这首歌献给“任何愿意反抗体制的人”。</p><p> “这是为那些愿意说‘你知道吗，我认为世界可以变得更好，我将有勇气大声说出来并反对那些刺痛的人，让这个世界对每个人来说都更美好’的人写的，”她说。添加。</p><p>乐队在将 Peaches 推上舞台之前，对这首歌进行了相当长的演绎，并将歌曲的其余部分与 Peaches 2000 年的歌曲“Fuck The Pain Away”混合在一起。</p><p> “亲爱的来宾，请为这位传奇的、无与伦比的、才华横溢的、性感的混蛋桃子举起双手，”曼森对观众说，欢迎客人上台。观看上面完整的时刻。</p><p> Garbage 的演出是在乐队透露今年他们一直在录音室制作新专辑后不久进行的。</p><p>这支由雪莉·曼森 (Shirley Manson) 领衔的乐队于 2021 年发行了他们的第七张也是最新的全长唱片<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/garbage-no-gods-no-masters-review-2963417">《No Gods No Masters》。</a> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/garbages-shirley-manson-interview-bleed-like-me-dave-grohl-new-album-industry-3614427">在最近接受<em>NME</em>采访时</a>，Garbage 反思了人们对这张 LP 的积极反应，并谈到了未来的发展。 </p><figure id="attachment_3772983" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3772983" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3772983" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Garbage@2000x1270.jpg" alt="苏格兰裔美国摇滚乐队 Garbage 的主唱雪莉·曼森 (Shirley Manson) 将于 2024 年在柏林演出" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Garbage@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Garbage@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Garbage@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Garbage@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Garbage@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/Garbage@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3772983" class="wp-caption-text"> 《Garbage》乐队的雪莉·曼森 (Shirley Manson) 将于 2024 年在柏林演出。图片来源：Pedro Becerra/Redferns/Getty</figcaption></figure><p> “我真的很高兴‘无神无主’受到如此好评，因为我们没有任何期望，”曼森解释道。 “进入下一张专辑时，我感觉到了一种转变。我正在努力平息我的愤怒。作为一个社会，我们已经变得如此沮丧和心碎。我正在努力争取比我更大一点的东西，因为如果我不这样做，我就会被自己的沮丧淹没。”</p><p>当被问及这种沮丧感从何而来时， <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/the-big-interview-nme-icon-shirley-manson-on-the-metoo-movement-dolores-oriordan-and-the-future-of-garbage-2241063">这位<em>《NME</em>偶像奖》获得者</a>谈到了<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/garbage-3-1198200">2016 年从舞台上摔下来</a>后接受髋关节置换术的经历，她说这导致了“难以忍受的疼痛”。</p><p>她还将 Garbage 的下一张专辑描述为“探照灯”，并补充道：“在烧焦大地之后，我们带着探照灯走出了一个肮脏的洞穴。我们正在寻找生命和人性的碎片。”</p><p>至于歌迷何时可以听到乐队的新唱片，曼森告诉<em>《NME》</em> ：“实际上，我们说话的时候就在录音室里。预计五月底完成，我们已经达到目标了。”</p><p>在接受<em>NME</em>采访时， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/garbages-shirley-manson-on-when-their-label-once-chose-to-invest-in-no-doubt-over-them-it-was-devastating-3749509">曼森谈到了 Garbage 厂牌选择投资 No Doubt 的“毁灭性”时刻</a>。她还<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/garbages-shirley-manson-calls-dave-grohl-the-most-incredible-expanse-of-joy-3749873">谈到了与喷火战机主唱戴夫·格罗尔（Dave Grohl）的合作</a>，称他为“最令人难以置信的欢乐”。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Garbage 的雪莉·曼森 (Shirley Manson)：“现在是改变现状的时候了”| 2018 年 VO5 NME 奖" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/AXze6tCxNEA?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> Garbage 本月早些时候发行了<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/garbage-announce-expanded-reissue-of-bleed-like-me-on-vinyl-and-more-3583953">2005 年专辑《Bleed Like Me》的扩展版重新</a>发行版。 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/garbage-announce-summer-2024-uk-and-european-tour-buy-tickets-3596330">今年夏天他们将继续他们的英国和欧洲巡演</a>，最后在伦敦温布利 OVO 体育场举行演出。 <a href="https://www.ticketmaster.co.uk/garbage-tickets/artist/776816?irgwc=1&amp;utm_source=2862475-NME%20Networks%20Media%20Limited&amp;utm_medium=affiliate&amp;utm_campaign=2862475&amp;awtrc=&amp;clickId=WVMWLAT55xyPTjiVXp0rVUKSUkH3PcUNnRXHRo0&amp;camefrom=CFC_BUYAT_2862475&amp;ircid=7559" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在此查找英国日期的所有剩余门票</a>。</p><p>此外，曼森等人。计划在格拉斯哥的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/trnsmt-2024-liam-gallagher-gerry-cinmamon-calvin-harris-lead-line-up-3545593">TRNSMT 音乐节</a>和马德里的<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/dua-lipa-pearl-jam-bring-me-the-horizon-lead-mad-cool-2024-line-up-3557226">Mad Cool</a>音乐节上亮相，后者将于本周晚些时候举行。</p><p>他们的支持乐队包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/savages">Savages</a>主唱<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/jehnny-beth">Jehnny Beth</a>和 Lucia &amp; The Best Boys。</p><p> Garbage <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/garbage-on-why-they-chose-these-support-acts-for-huge-2024-london-wembley-show-3762841">上个月宣布这一消息时</a>在 Instagram 上写道：“伟大偶像 Jehnny Beth 加入我们，参加 7 月 20 日在伦敦温布利 OVO 体育场举行的演出，我感到无比兴奋。” “你可能已经知道了——珍妮是一位神。除了苏格兰最优秀的另类摇滚乐队之一 Lucia &amp; The Best Boys 之外，她也将加入我们。”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-garbage-and-peaches-perform-push-it-and-fuck-the-pain-away-3772980">Watch Garbage 和 Peaches 在柏林表演“Push It”和“Fuck The Pain Away”混搭后，</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
莎朗·范·埃滕 (Sharon Van Etten) 宣布在伦敦举办一次性演出——她一年多以来的首次演出https://www.nme.com/news/music/sharon-van-etten-announces-one-off-london-show-her-first-performance-in-over-a-year-3772941?utm_source=rss&utm_medium= rss&utm_campaign=sharon-van-etten-宣布在伦敦举行一年多来的首次演出Tom SkinnerMon, 08 Jul 2024 15:40:23 +0000 Music NewsNewsIndieLive Music News https://www.nme.com/?p=3772941 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/SharonVanEtten-announces-one-off-London-live-show.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="Sharon Van Etten 现场表演" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/SharonVanEtten-announces-one-off-London-live-show.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/SharonVanEtten-announces-one-off-London-live-show-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/SharonVanEtten-announces-one-off-London-live-show-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/SharonVanEtten-announces-one-off-London-live-show-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/SharonVanEtten-announces-one-off-London-live-show-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/SharonVanEtten-announces-one-off-London-live-show-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “嘘，别告诉任何人！”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sharon-van-etten-announces-one-off-london-show-her-first-performance-in-over-a-year-3772941">Sharon Van Etten 宣布将在伦敦举行一次性演出——她一年多来的首次表演</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/SharonVanEtten-announces-one-off-London-live-show.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="Sharon Van Etten 现场表演" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/SharonVanEtten-announces-one-off-London-live-show.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/SharonVanEtten-announces-one-off-London-live-show-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/SharonVanEtten-announces-one-off-London-live-show-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/SharonVanEtten-announces-one-off-London-live-show-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/SharonVanEtten-announces-one-off-London-live-show-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/07/SharonVanEtten-announces-one-off-London-live-show-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sharon-van-etten">莎朗·范·埃滕 (Sharon Van Etten)</a>宣布在伦敦举办一场一次性演出，这是她一年多来的首次现场表演。</p><p>这位新泽西歌手兼作曲家于 2022 年 5 月发行了她的第六张也是最新的录音室专辑<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/sharon-van-etten-weve-been-going-about-this-all-wrong-3218530">《We’ve Been Going About This All Wrong》。</a>去年，她分享了<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/film-reviews/past-lives-review-a24-greta-lee-3495175"><em>《前世今生》</em></a>原声带中的<a href="https://youtu.be/BPt0xSNfwCs" target="_blank" rel="noopener">《安静的眼睛》</a>和考特尼· <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sharon-van-etten-shares-emotive-new-single-close-to-you-co-written-by-courtney-barnett-3528301">巴尼特 (Courtney Barnett) 合作的</a>歌曲。 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sharon-van-etten-shares-emotive-new-single-close-to-you-co-written-by-courtney-barnett-3528301">创作单曲《靠近你》</a> 。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/big-reads/sharon-van-etten-cover-interview-2022-weve-been-going-about-this-all-wrong-3204585">Sharon Van Etten：“我必须充满希望。我是一名母亲，我想为了我的儿子勇敢”</a></strong></li></ul><p>据<a href="https://www.setlist.fm/setlists/sharon-van-etten-43d413fb.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Setlist.FM 报道</em></a>，Van Etten 自 2023 年春季以来就没有参加过演出。今天（7 月 8 日），这位《Seventeen》歌手在社交媒体上透露，她很快就会重返舞台。</p><p> “嗨，我是莎伦，”她在一段简短的视频中开始说道，“我有一个小秘密。”</p><p> Van Etten 继续说道：“我和乐队在伦敦，我们将于 7 月 17 日演出。但如果你想了解更多详细信息，你必须注册我的电子邮件列表。”</p><p>她指着下巴开玩笑说：“希望到时候我的痘痘就消失了。嘘，别告诉任何人！”</p><p>即将举行的演出地点尚未确定。您可以<a href="https://sharonvanetten.ck.page/ac0988f540" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在此处注册以获取更多信息</a>，并查看下面的公告。</p><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="550" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">有关所有详细信息和获取门票： <a href="https://t.co/RrI4sojkfs">https://t.co/RrI4sojkfs</a> <img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/15.0.3/72x72/2764.png" alt="❤" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /><img src="https://s.w.org/images/core/emoji/15.0.3/72x72/1f39f.png" alt="🎟" class="wp-smiley" style="height: 1em; max-height: 1em;" /> <a href="https://t.co/j1VtnAONhQ">pic.twitter.com/j1VtnAONhQ</a></p><p> — 莎朗·范·埃滕 (@sharonvanetten) <a href="https://twitter.com/sharonvanetten/status/1810314732689342677?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">2024 年 7 月 8 日</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></p><p> Van Etten 尚未宣布任何新材料，但在今年年初与 Warner Chappell Music 签署了全球出版协议（来自<a href="https://www.musicweek.com/publishing/read/sharon-van-etten-signs-to-warner-chappell/089117#:~:text=As%20well%20as%20being%20an,the%20A24%20film%20Past%20Lives." target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>音乐周</em></a>）。 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sharon-van-etten-shares-her-new-single-porta-and-announces-uk-tour-3156428">她最近的英国演出于 2022 年举行，</a>当时她在布里克斯顿学院 (Brixton Academy) 担任主角。</p><p>去年 12 月， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/billie-eilish-dua-lipa-olivia-rodrigo-oscars-2024-shortlist-best-original-song-3562452">Van Etten 的歌曲《Quiet Eyes》入围 2024 年奥斯卡最佳原创歌曲奖</a>。该奖项<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/billie-eilish-nightmare-second-oscars-win-3599354">最终颁给了比莉·艾利什和芬尼斯的《我为何而生？》</a>来自<a href="https://www.nme.com/films/barbie"><em>芭比</em></a>。</p><p>最近，Van Etten 正在庆祝她 2014 年专辑<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/reviews-sharon-van-etten-15326-309746">《Are We There》</a>发行 10 周年。 </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Sharon Van Etten 与 Nick Cave 合作新专辑《We&#39;ve Been Going About This All Wrong》谈话中" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/gdZH55j_KGc?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" referrerpolicy="strict-origin-when-cross-origin" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> <em>NME</em> <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/sharon-van-etten-weve-been-going-about-this-all-wrong-3218530">在回顾 2022 年的《我们一直在做这一切都错了》时</a>写道：“最出色的《错误》是 Van Etten 的最佳作品，其震撼人心的副歌非常适合消除因封锁而引发的对遗憾的沉思 […]</p><p> “虽然它缺乏 2018 年热门歌曲<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/sharon-van-etten-remind-tomorrow-2431661">《Remind Me Tomorrow》</a>的即时性，但这张不屈不挠的唱片有时是对不确定时代的有力清算。”</p><p>您可以重温上面<em>NME</em>对 Sharon Van Etten 的视频采访。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/sharon-van-etten-announces-one-off-london-show-her-first-performance-in-over-a-year-3772941">Sharon Van Etten 宣布将在伦敦举行一次性演出——她一年多来的首次表演</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
